replies.bodyText:
As I understand now the symbol property means that a unit has a symbol directly attached to it. For derived units this should be null, and toString should implement the display of the derived symbol.
The test complying with this convertion should look like this:
assertNull(SmartHomeUnits.VAR_HOUR.getSymbol());
@cweitkamp  please let me know if you would like me to change the tests this way.
